==Useful Info==
'''Giant mites''' are [[poison]]ous [[cling]]ing vermin found on [[Dungeon]]:2 and lower. They're only slightly more dangerous than [[rat]]s and other early threats.

==Tips & Tricks==
*Although weak, a giant mite's poison can be enough to finish off a new character who hasn't found any [[potions of curing]] yet. Fragile or weakened characters should be cautious when engaging them in melee.

==History==
Giant mites were removed in [[0.17]].

